\par }{\b \'a7i\'d2u 1.
\par }{Ph\'b9m vi \'b8p d\'f4ng.
\par Hi\'d6p \'ae\'denh n\'b5y \'ae\'ad\'eec \'b8p d\'f4ng cho c\'b8c \'ae\'e8i t\'ad\'eeng l\'b5 nh\'f7ng \'ae\'e8i t\'ad\'eeng c\'ad tr\'f3 c\'f1a m\'e9t ho\'c6c c\'f1a c\'b6 hai N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t.
\par }{\b \'a7i\'d2u 2.
\par }{C\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 bao g\'e5m trong Hi\'d6p \'ae\'denh:
\par 1. Hi\'d6p \'ae\'denh n\'b5y \'b8p d\'f4ng \'ae\'e8i v\'edi c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 do m\'e9t N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t ho\'c6c c\'b8c c\'ac quan ch\'ddnh quy\'d2n c\'ac s\'eb hay ch\'ddnh quy\'d2n \'ae\'dea ph\'ad\'acng c\'f1a N\'ad\'edc \'ae\'e3, \'ae\'b8
nh v\'b5o thu nh\'cbp, b\'cat k\'d3 h\'d7nh th\'f8c \'b8p d\'f4ng c\'f1a c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 \'ae\'e3 nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5o.
\par 2. T\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 thu tr\'aan t\'e6ng thu nh\'cbp, ho\'c6c nh\'f7ng ph\'c7n c\'f1a thu nh\'cbp; bao g\'e5m c\'b8c kho\'b6n thu\'d5 \'ae\'e8i v\'edi l\'eei t\'f8c t\'f5 vi\'d6c chuy\'d3n nh\'ad\'eeng \'ae\'e9ng s\'b6n ho\'c6c b\'cat 
\'ae\'e9ng s\'b6n, thu\'d5 \'ae\'b8nh tr\'aan t\'e6ng s\'e8 ti\'d2n l\'ad\'acng ho\'c6c ti\'d2n c\'abng do x\'dd nghi\'d6p chi tr\'b6 c\'f2ng nh\'ad c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 \'ae\'b8nh tr\'aan ph\'c7n gi\'b8 tr\'de t\'b5i s\'b6n t\'a8ng th\'aam \'ae\'d2u 
\'ae\'ad\'eec coi l\'b5 thu\'d5 \'ae\'b8nh v\'b5o thu nh\'cbp.
\par 3. Nh\'f7ng lo\'b9i thu\'d5 hi\'d6n h\'b5nh \'ae\'ad\'eec \'b8p d\'f4ng trong Hi\'d6p \'ae\'denh n\'b5y l\'b5:
\par a.  T\'b9i Vi\'d6t Nam:
\par (i). Thu\'d5 thu nh\'cbp c\'b8 nh\'a9n;
\par (ii).Thu\'d5 l\'eei t\'f8c; v\'b5
\par (iii).Thu\'d5 chuy\'d3n l\'eei nhu\'cbn ra n\'ad\'edc ngo\'b5i;
\par (D\'ad\'edi \'ae\'a9y \'ae\'ad\'eec g\'e4i l\'b5 \ldblquote thu\'d5 Vi\'d6t Nam\rdblquote );
\par b. T\'b9i L\'b5o:
\par (i). Thu\'d5 thu nh\'cbp c\'b8 nh\'a9n;
\par (ii). Thu\'d5 l\'eei t\'f8c;
\par  (D\'ad\'edi \'ae\'a9y g\'e4i l\'b5 \ldblquote thu\'d5 L\'b5o \ldblquote )
\par 4. Hi\'d6p \'ae\'denh n\'b5y c\'f2ng s\'cf \'ae\'ad\'eec \'b8p d\'f4ng cho c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 c\'e3 t\'ddnh ch\'cat t\'ad\'acng t\'f9 hay v\'d2 c\'a8n b\'b6n gi\'e8ng nh\'ad c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 tr\'aan \'ae\'ad\'eec ban h\'b5nh sau ng\'b5y k\'fd k
\'d5t Hi\'d6p \'ae\'denh n\'b5y \'ae\'d3 b\'e6 sung, ho\'c6c thay th\'d5 c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 hi\'d6n h\'b5nh. C\'b8c nh\'b5 ch\'f8c tr\'b8ch c\'e3 th\'c8m quy\'d2n c\'f1a c\'b8c N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t s\'cf th\'abng b\'b8o cho nhau nh\'f7ng thay \'ae
\'e6i quan tr\'e4ng  trong  lu\'cbt thu\'d5 c\'f1a t\'f5ng N\'ad\'edc.
\par }{\b \'a7i\'d2u 3.
\par }{C\'b8c \'ae\'denh ngh\'dca chung:
\par 1. Theo n\'e9i dung c\'f1a Hi\'d6p \'ae\'denh n\'b5y, tr\'f5 tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep ng\'f7 c\'b6nh \'ae\'dfi h\'e1i m\'e9t s\'f9 gi\'b6i th\'ddch kh\'b8c:
\par a.\ldblquote Vi\'d6t Nam\rdblquote  c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 n\'ad\'edc C\'e9ng ho\'b5 x\'b7 h\'e9i ch\'f1 ngh\'dca Vi\'d6t Nam; 
\par b. \ldblquote L\'b5o\rdblquote  c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 n\'ad\'edc C\'e9ng ho\'b5 D\'a9n ch\'f1 Nh\'a9n d\'a9n L\'b5o;
\par  c. Thu\'cbt ng\'f7 \ldblquote N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t\rdblquote  v\'b5 \ldblquote N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t kia\rdblquote  c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 Vi\'d6t Nam hay L\'b5o tu\'fa theo ng\'f7 c\'b6nh \'ae\'dfi h\'e1i;
\par d.  Thu\'cbt ng\'f7 \ldblquote \'ae\'e8i t\'ad\'eeng\rdblquote  bao g\'e5m c\'b8 nh\'a9n, c\'abng ty hay b\'cat k\'fa t\'e6 ch\'f8c nhi\'d2u \'ae\'e8i t\'ad\'eeng;
\par e. Thu\'cbt ng\'f7 \ldblquote c\'abng ty\rdblquote  \'ae\'d3 ch\'d8 c\'b8c t\'e6 ch\'f8c c\'abng ty ho\'c6c b\'cat  k\'fa m\'e9t th\'f9c th\'d3 n\'b5o \'ae\'ad\'eec coi l\'b5 t\'e6 ch\'f8c c\'abng ty d\'ad\'edi gi\'b8c \'ae\'e9 thu\'d5;
\par f. Thu\'cbt ng\'f7 \ldblquote x\'dd nghi\'d6p c\'f1a N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t\rdblquote  v\'b5 \ldblquote x\'dd nghi\'d6p c\'f1a N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t kia\rdblquote  theo th\'f8 t\'f9  c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 m\'e9t x\'dd nghi\'d6p \'ae\'ad\'eec \'aei\'d2
u h\'b5nh b\'ebi \'ae\'e8i t\'ad\'eeng c\'ad tr\'f3 c\'f1a m\'e9t N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t v\'b5 m\'e9t x\'dd nghi\'d6p \'ae\'ad\'eec \'aei\'d2u h\'b5nh b\'ebi \'ae\'e8i t\'ad\'eeng c\'ad tr\'f3 c\'f1a N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t  kia;
\par g. Thu\'cbt ng\'f7 \ldblquote \'ae\'e8i t\'ad\'eeng mang qu\'e8c t\'dech\rdblquote  c\'e3 ngh\'dca:
\par  (i). C\'b8c c\'b8 nh\'a9n mang qu\'e8c t\'dech c\'f1a m\'e9t N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t; hay
\par (ii). C\'b8c ph\'b8p nh\'a9n, t\'e6 ch\'f8c h\'efn v\'e8n v\'b5 hi\'d6p h\'e9i c\'e3 t\'ad c\'b8ch \'ae\'ad\'eec ch\'cap nh\'cbn theo c\'b8c lu\'cbt c\'e3 hi\'d6u l\'f9c t\'b9i m\'e9t N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t;
\par h. Thu\'cbt ng\'f7 \ldblquote v\'cbn t\'b6i qu\'e8c t\'d5\rdblquote  c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 b\'cat c\'f8 s\'f9 v\'cbn chuy\'d3n n\'b5o b\'bbng t\'b5u thu\'fb ho\'c6c m\'b8y bay \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'f9c hi\'d6n b\'ebi m\'e9t x\'dd nghi\'d6p c\'e3 tr\'f4 s\'eb 
